Skip syncing
.I work_stories.md
and
.I candidate_context.md
before generation.
.TP
.I JD_SOURCE
Job description URL or local file path.
.TP
.I COMPANY
Optional company slug override.
.TP
.I ROLE
Optional role slug override.
.SS pipeline
.TP
.BI --provider " {claude|codex}"
LLM provider to use for asset generation and submit-time answers.
.TP
.B --skip-sync
Skip syncing
.I work_stories.md
and
.I candidate_context.md
before generation.
.TP
.BI --browser-provider " {local|steel}"
Browser runtime to use for the submit automation stage.
.TP
.B --payload-only
Generate the board-specific autofill payload after assets are built, but do not launch the browser.
.TP
.B --headless
Run the submit automation stage in headless mode.
.TP
.B --submit
Submit the application after autofill. Without this flag, the runtime stops at a review state.
.TP
.I JD_SOURCE
Job description URL or local file path.
.TP
.I COMPANY
Optional company slug override.
.TP
.I ROLE
Optional role slug override.
.SS batch
.TP
.B --dry-run
List matching jobs without processing them.
.TP
