Maximum number of concurrent LLM jobs for the shared batch worker pool.
.TP
.BI --provider " {claude|codex}"
LLM provider to use for content generation.
.SS submit
.TP
.I TARGET
Existing output directory or matching job URL to submit through the supported board runtime.
.TP
.B --payload-only
Only generate the board-specific autofill payload without launching the browser.
.TP
.B --headless
Run the board submitter in headless mode.
.TP
.B --submit
Submit the application after autofill. Without this flag, the runtime stops at a review state.
.TP
.BI --provider " {claude|codex}"
LLM provider to use for generated open-ended application answers.
.SS parallel
.TP
.B --dry-run
List matching jobs without processing them.
.TP
.B --build-only
Skip LLM generation and only build documents for jobs that already have final content files.
.TP
.BI --max-parallel " N"
Maximum number of concurrent LLM jobs.
.TP
.BI --provider " {claude|codex}"
LLM provider to use for content generation.
.SS profile
.TP
.I show
Print the current contents of
.IR application_profile.md .
.TP
.I path
Print the path to
