.SS notion-sync
.TP
.I TARGET
Output directory or matching job URL to sync into Notion.
.TP
.BI --wait-for-email " N"
Seconds to wait for the matching confirmation email before leaving the sync pending.
.TP
.B --allow-pending-email
Exit successfully when the website confirmation exists but the confirmation email has not arrived yet.
.TP
.B --strict-token
Exit non-zero when
.B NOTION_API_TOKEN
is missing instead of writing a pending sync status artifact.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.local/bin
Recommended install location for command symlinks.
.TP
.I /opt/homebrew/share/man/man1
Default install location for man page symlinks on this machine.
.TP
.I output/<company>/<role>/
Role root containing
.IR content/ ,
.IR documents/ ,
and
.IR submit/
subdirectories plus
.IR .pipeline_meta.json .
.TP
.I application_profile.md
Editable application-form defaults for work authorization, sponsorship, compensation/salary-comfort gates, text-message consent, hearing-about-us answers, LinkedIn, GitHub, website URLs, pronouns, and voluntary self-identification answers.
.TP
.I .env.local
Gitignored repo-local environment file. The CLI and shared scripts auto-load it for persistent secrets such as
.BR NOTION_API_TOKEN .
.TP
.I output/<company>/<role>/submit/notion_sync_status.json
Status artifact for automatic or manual Notion application sync attempts.
